If you don't mind.

01:50.880 --> 01:52.520
OK. Fine.
Thanks so much.

01:53.640 --> 01:56.599
Hi. Anna's gonna drop you off
at Nana's.

01:56.600 --> 01:58.919
Be good, OK? See you tomorrow.

