02:00.680 --> 02:03.200
I'll text you when...
Hi, Larry. Where are you?

02:04.160 --> 02:06.080
We're on in an hour.

02:07.400 --> 02:09.039
Mm-hm.

02:09.040 --> 02:10.280
Mm-hm.

