Really?
Come on.

02:42.560 --> 02:43.800
Happy birthday, darling.

02:45.560 --> 02:47.079
Thank you.

02:47.080 --> 02:48.320
Roy?

02:53.080 --> 02:56.240
I had no idea you had so many.

02:57.320 --> 02:58.959
